She stood up and looked at Iron Raptor and Prowl.  "I...I'll be ok. I 
just want to walk for a bit if you don't mind. Iron Raptor, I shall 
go as you have requested."  She took a few steps and came face to 
face with Prowl.  She looked down and walked past him, with her arms 
still around her.  She walked slowly down the hall and towards the 
mess hall.  

Arcangle startled her. She jumped and swiped her claws at him, 
missing him by a few inches. She took a step back when she saw she 
almost clawed him. Her face showed fear towards him.  "OH!  I'm..I'm 
sorry. You scared me."  She turned and walked down the hall with her 
head lowed.
